## 12. Appendix

### Glossary

|  |  |
| --- | --- |
| Term | Definition |
| QuickPick | VS CodeвҖҷs built-in list selection UI component |
| Component | TypeScript interface representing an injectable resource set |
| INDEXER\_OPTIONS | Array of 5 Component objects for indexer languages |
| INDEXER\_BASE | Component object for base config (always copied) |
| Filtered Copy | Copy only whitelisted items from a directory |
| Recursive Copy | Copy entire directory tree, skipping excluded dirs |

